title: Must Love Dogs
description:
This week's episode, all we ask is that you must love dogs and have a little bit of a sixth sense, but what’s new? June has some good news about her dog Sgt Meatball and reveals she will be speaking plainly from here on out. Meanwhile, Jessica is now a pro at fake eyelashes and we think this is HUGE news. Deep Divers, remember to come as you are, even if that means you're a Susan or are currently being Susan'd. 


For more information on how to support the people of Ukraine

https://wck.org/world  

https://outrightinternational.org/ukraine

Amnesty International 

More info on how to help African refugees and the LGBTQIA communities in Ukraine 

https://www.self.com/story/ukraine-refugees-black-lgbtq

If you can't afford to donate, you can stay informed at @kyivindependant_official or https://kyivindependent.com/

You can follow The Deep Dive on Twitter @thedeepdivepod
